name: Bainbridge, Appellant, v. Merchants and Miners Transportation Co.
name_abbreviation: Bainbridge v. Merchants & Miners Transportation Co.

judges: Before Frazer, C. J., Simpson, Kephart, Schaerer, Maxey and Drew, JJ.
parties: Bainbridge, Appellant, v. Merchants and Miners Transportation Co.

opinions.text:
Per Curiam,
The order of the court below dismissing this action for want of jurisdiction is affirmed on the opinion of Judge Finletter, which clearly and adequately discusses the question involved.
Judgment affirmed.
